  <summary date="2022-01-18T23:18:51Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Preventing Mandates on Toddlers Act

This bill prohibits federal funds from being used to implement or enforce the Department of Health and Human Services' rule titled Vaccine and Mask Requirements To Mitigate the Spread of COVID-19 in Head Start Programs, published on November 30, 2021, or any substantially similar rule, regulation, or agency statement.</summary>
